{"tid":741874,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登所有高層，CEO ，一齊入黎開會！","createTime":"2018-07-14T05:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T08:44:48.000Z","uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e96ce7442bfef90e58ff0cdfc098a3ed37ed779c","tid":741874,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T05:34:28.000Z","msg":"我係連登高級首席分析師 (CEA) (Chief Executive Analyst) <br />\n<br />\n老實講，我唔太睇好香港經濟既前景 <br />\n我大陸果塊地，考慮緊都要放出去<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n我聽我秘書講，佢話我知大家樂食個餐都成七八十蚊<br />\n我預計基層市民都捱唔到幾耐 <br />\n個經濟遲早爆煲<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇香港前景？"},{"pid":"90dbce894dc9f449bc62cecf102b70e2489d7fd5","tid":741874,"uid":36670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T05:36:39.000Z","msg":"一日未升廿三條，我估佢都唔會冧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859c50441f8b26e494fcc50632932277e663c160","tid":741874,"uid":36670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一日未立廿三條，我估佢都唔會冧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fef77ab886824a52424f29dd96db4953eb6ed8bb","tid":741874,"uid":41737,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T05:39:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d06a807567a2c0723c2590985502c71e3b701d94","tid":741874,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fef77ab886824a52424f29dd96db4953eb6ed8bb","tid":741874,"uid":41737,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T05:39:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T05:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b8df94f5db80f4a18b1a581f53f2e181dc611d","tid":741874,"uid":189053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T05:52:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3f5e22